name: Rabbit Rescue (prauraa)
description:
Rabbit Rescue - A game where you separate rabbits from the other infected rabbits to save them from getting infected. And you do this in a very fun way!

Play Rabbit-Rescue on Liluo - https://liluo.io/pr851/rabbit-rescue

Known bugs - When the left click is pressed rigorously without any movement may cause rabbits to jump weirdly.
